title: Mumbai Lamb Rump & Curry Sauce with Bombay Roasted Kumara & Garlic Baby Veggie
description: A soft breeze, a warm summer day and a slice of succulent lamb rump are all you need to tie together one great dinner. But why not add a few tasty extras like a Bengali sauce and why not add a warm touch to the kumara by roasting it in mustard seeds.

